<plot>Sonia, is a woman locked inside a motel room waiting for her lover. Hopeless and certain that he will never show up, Sonia decides to kill herself, but first she will seek consolation in the songs of her favorite romantic singer and on the ear of her best friend, Maria Eunice. But what Sonia does not know is that her first call will not be her last but will in fact set the tone of this comedy of errors with great performances and an unexpected ending.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?035456</url></doc>
